headline: Three Reasons Investors Love Rollins (ROL)
summary: Over the past six months, Rollins’s shares (currently trading at $46.60) have posted a disappointing 5.7% loss, well below the S&P 500’s 10% gain. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
